geometric interpretation of

00:17:08.180 --> 00:17:09.350
what's going on here.

00:17:09.350 --> 00:17:13.680
That is, that we went a distance
alpha along this arc.

00:17:13.680 --> 00:17:28.570
And now remember that the
radius here is 1.

00:17:28.570 --> 00:17:34.430
And this horizontal distance
here is a.

00:17:34.430 --> 00:17:37.450
This distance here is a.

00:17:37.450 --> 00:17:43.710
