interpretation of this is that

00:17:43.710 --> 00:17:51.000
this angle is alpha radians.

00:17:51.000 --> 00:17:54.950
And sine alpha = a.

00:17:54.950 --> 00:17:58.480
So this is consistent with our
definition previously, our

00:17:58.480 --> 00:18:02.530
