00:18:12.570 --> 00:18:14.770
This is the first time
you're deriving it.

00:18:14.770 --> 00:18:18.420
This is the first time you're
seeing it correctly done.

00:18:18.420 --> 00:18:20.780
And furthermore, this is the
first time you're seeing a

00:18:20.780 --> 00:18:24.100
