00:18:37.040 --> 00:18:40.900
what radians are, you have
to calculate this number.

00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:44.070
If you've calculated this number
then by definition if

00:18:44.070 --> 00:18:49.280
sine is the thing whose alpha
radian amount gives you a,

00:18:49.280 --> 00:18:52.520
then it must be that this
