00:38:34.550 --> 00:38:41.400
And there is, if you use
vertical slices as we did

00:38:41.400 --> 00:38:45.710
here, that is, well they're sort
of tips of slices, it's a

00:38:45.710 --> 00:38:46.790
different idea.

00:38:46.790 --> 00:38:50.910
But anyway, it's using dx as the
integral of the variable

00:38:50.910 --> 00:38:52.670
of integration.

00:38:52.670 --> 00:38:55.800
So we're checking each little
piece, each little

00:38:55.800 --> 00:38:58.750
strip of that type.

00:38:58.750 --> 00:39:00.540
If we use dx here,
we get this.

00:39:00.540 --> 00:39:03.130
If you did the same thing
rotated the other way, and use

00:39:03.130 --> 00:39:06.140
dy as the variable, you get
