00:39:08.120 --> 00:39:14.080
Because they're parallel.

00:39:14.080 --> 00:39:14.870
So you're, yep.

00:39:14.870 --> 00:39:17.280
STUDENT: [INAUDIBLE]

00:39:17.280 --> 00:39:19.770
PROFESSOR: Can you do service
area with shells?

00:39:19.770 --> 00:39:23.330
Well, ah shell shape.

00:39:23.330 --> 00:39:26.540
The short answer is not quite.

00:39:26.540 --> 00:39:32.340
The shell shape is a vertical
