00:39:32.340 --> 00:39:34.850
three-dimensional, and
it has a thickness.

00:39:34.850 --> 00:39:37.270
So this is just a matter
of terminology, though.

00:39:37.270 --> 00:39:41.210
This thickness is this dx, when
